modules.description: This module provides functions to construct and manipulate Dune build configuration expressions, such as declaring libraries, executables, and tests. It works with symbolic representations of Dune syntax trees, allowing precise control over build descriptions. Concrete use cases include generating Dune files with dynamic library dependencies or custom build rules based on external configuration.
